{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"胸中的秘密被顯示的時侯"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"在那日, 他們的主, 確是徹知他們的。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"大難"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"大難是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你怎能知道大難是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"在那日, 眾人將似分散的飛蛾"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"山岳將似疏松的釆絨。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"至於善功的份量較重者"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"將在滿意的生活中"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"至於善功的份量較輕者"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"他的歸宿是深坑。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"你怎能知道深坑裏有什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"有烈火。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"競賽富庶, 已使你們疏忽"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"直到你們去遊墳地。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"真的, 你們將來就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"真的, 你們將來就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"真的, 假若你們有真知灼見, (你們必不疏忽)"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你們必定看見火獄"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"然後, 你們必親眼看見它。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日, 你們必為恩澤而被審問。"}]}